{"tid":1401362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前線要去抗爭要記得最重要嘅一點 不被捕","createTime":"2019-08-03T14:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T15:00:50.000Z","uid":167878,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f1777c45f5a1d7741e92f8264c82a5d8c87061e4","tid":1401362,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:39:50.000Z","msg":"而家香港人已經做到不分化 不割席<br />\n基本上你地做乜都唔會有人指責你地<br />\n<br />\n所以而家你地每次出去抗爭<br />\n最重要嘅目標就係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比人捉</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唯有搵到越高回報低成本嘅抗爭方法<br />\n出嚟抗爭嘅人先會越嚟越多"},{"pid":"8e7fc2301f09e1338ce92804dcf19a82c85ec73d","tid":1401362,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:40:03.000Z","msg":"不留守"},{"pid":"f83b49e1aad4a954b82976cce67145ef1e972cfe","tid":1401362,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:40:13.000Z","msg":"不被捕"},{"pid":"893f7f703ef399d2b9da5216428f44725961fa12","tid":1401362,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:40:23.000Z","msg":"最重要係唔好比人捉"},{"pid":"b81ecae3facbd5d0dccdb294a1ebcea22239f5a2","tid":1401362,"uid":235374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:40:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n前線有鬼？？？有勇無謀？？？唔知真假<br />\n我懷疑有狗混入 叫大家留係到<br />\n已經講左成個禮拜be water<br />\n唔好理佢地 現場要走快d走<br />\n去咩黃大仙 狗要追上你可以好快<br />\n唔好慢慢行 要跑！！！！地鐵巴士都得</span></span>"},{"pid":"c086917419a1015e9d57cb8013b3a6825d42179a","tid":1401362,"uid":265935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:40:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>逃生路線 (已整合)<br />\n<br />\n尖沙咀：向尖東方向/紅磡Poly<br />\n<br />\n佐敦：東向經漆咸道南去紅磡poly<br />\n<br />\n旺角：經洗衣街 染布房街上窩打老道 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">亞皆老街x染布房街有人高空擲物</span></strong><br />\n培正道轉右上何文田 再經佛光街落地鐵 / 紅磡<br />\n<br />\n何文田有地鐵可以走<br />\n<br />\n油麻地：地鐵、經天橋櫻桃街公園去奧海城 （小心果欄條路多狗車 勿近）（奧海城奶共，自行考慮)<br />\n如果唔想入奶共奧海城，可以行去海旁行多10分鐘去南昌。<br />\n<br />\n補充加多條九龍城，先達廣場出直行往旺角東天橋，可散入何文田，仲可以入九龍城，如果識路，入九龍仔公園民生書院果頭，非常多位呢<br />\n</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"a241fe647b816deab933f332f355f4512c010f33","tid":1401362,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:40:42.000Z","msg":"前線係最重要"},{"pid":"3f0585cde6aba3df5ca0e92ddbf36ab087f24d84","tid":1401362,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:41:05.000Z","msg":"唔可以再損失"},{"pid":"a8c6460d61879b4b40831c45a4cb87716c011eea","tid":1401362,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:41:33.000Z","msg":"我愛前線"},{"pid":"0a63399f03d291b78ac110969024e18efbaeaab8","tid":1401362,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:41:43.000Z","msg":"香港人愛前線"},{"pid":"5b8209d91ff43acb50365a1b6c90e438c516b3b0","tid":1401362,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:42:01.000Z","msg":"唔好比人捉"},{"pid":"b4fefc293d4af41f0f5ecf0939ba027bad53a597","tid":1401362,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:42:16.000Z","msg":"高回報低風險"},{"pid":"06fe47b32a11e093bdcd0f931b68ae2ef85573ed","tid":1401362,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:42:25.000Z","msg":"有鬼啊<br />\n自己定幾點走<br />\n唔好理其他人<br />\n堅守不被捕"},{"pid":"5361b094664155d3c907edafeaf29686f56845a6","tid":1401362,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:42:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">麻包袋</span></span>"},{"pid":"9e1d37315f5d363e1dc7b6f2f607ea367fd84bf6","tid":1401362,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:43:06.000Z","msg":"無謂留守街道"},{"pid":"a7eb7d923a2954eed7eaa227b13316539ca898f4","tid":1401362,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03